---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Learn Lab | Nền tảng luyện thi TOEIC, IELTS & Cambridge thông minh">
  <main class="w-full overflow-hidden font-sans">
    
    <section class="relative pt-28 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-teal-50 via-white to-white"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-teal-100 bg-teal-50/50 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-teal-700 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500 animate-pulse"></span>
          Cập nhật thuật toán Flashcard 2.0
        </div>

        <h1 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-[1.15]">
          Làm chủ tiếng Anh <br class="hidden sm:block" />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-emerald-500">
            dễ dàng hơn bao giờ hết.
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-xl">
          Nền tảng luyện thi TOEIC, IELTS & Cambridge ứng dụng <strong class="text-slate-900">Spaced Repetition</strong> và <strong class="text-slate-900">AI Dictation</strong>. Tối ưu thời gian, tăng điểm thần tốc.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="/english-lab/toeic" class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-teal-600 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-teal-200 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-teal-700 active:scale-95 sm:w-auto">
            Bắt đầu học miễn phí
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/free-resources" class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-slate-700 transition-all hover:border-teal-600 hover:text-teal-600 sm:w-auto">
            Nhận tài liệu Free
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-3">
          <div class="flex -space-x-3">
            <img class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=1" alt="User" />
            <img class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=2" alt="User" />
            <img class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=3" alt="User" />
            <img class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full border-2 border-white object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=4" alt="User" />
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-white bg-slate-100 text-xs font-bold text-slate-600">+10k</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Được tin dùng bởi hơn <span class="text-slate-800">10,000+</span> học viên mỗi ngày</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-100">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Hệ sinh thái English Lab</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 font-medium">Ba trụ cột giúp bạn phát triển toàn diện cả Từ vựng, Kỹ năng Nghe và Chiến thuật làm bài.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          
          <a href="/english-lab/toeic/flashcards" class="group relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-100 overflow-hidden text-left block">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-32 h-32 text-teal-600"><path d="M4.5 3.75a3 3 0 00-3 3v.75h21v-.75a3 3 0 00-3-3h-15z" /><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M22.5 9.75h-21v7.5a3 3 0 003 3h15a3 3 0 003-3v-7.5zm-18 3.75a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h6a.75.75 0 010 1.5h-6a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75zm.75 2.25a.75.75 0 000 1.5h3a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-3z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-600 group-hover:bg-teal-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="h-7 w-7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0112 21 8.25 8.25 0 016.038 7.048 8.287 8.287 0 009 9.6a8.983 8.983 0 013.361-6.867 8.21 8.21 0 003 2.48z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18a3.75 3.75 0 00.495-7.467 5.99 5.99 0 00-1.925 3.546 5.974 5.974 0 01-2.133-1A3.75 3.75 0 0012 18z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">Smart Flashcards</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium mb-6">
              Học từ vựng với thẻ lật 3D. Tích hợp từ đồng nghĩa và thuật toán lặp lại ngắt quãng giúp nhớ lâu gấp 3 lần.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
              Học từ vựng ngay &rarr;
            </span>
          </a>

          <a href="/english-lab/toeic/dictation" class="group relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-sky-100 overflow-hidden text-left block">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-32 h-32 text-sky-600"><path d="M13.5 4.06c0-1.336-1.616-2.005-2.56-1.06l-4.5 4.5H4.508c-1.141 0-2.318.664-2.66 1.905A9.76 9.76 0 001.5 12c0 .898.121 1.768.35 2.595.341 1.24 1.518 1.905 2.659 1.905h1.93l4.5 4.5c.945.945 2.561.276 2.561-1.06V4.06zM18.584 5.106a.75.75 0 011.06 0c3.808 3.807 3.808 9.98 0 13.788a.75.75 0 11-1.06-1.06 8.25 8.25 0 000-11.668.75.75 0 010-1.06z" /><path d="M15.932 7.757a.75.75 0 011.061 0 4.5 4.5 0 010 6.364.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06 3 3 0 000-4.243.75.75 0 010-1.061z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-50 text-sky-600 group-hover:bg-sky-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="h-7 w-7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors">Pro Dictation</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium mb-6">
              Nghe chép chính tả từng câu với hệ thống Live-check lỗi ngay khi gõ. Tùy chỉnh tốc độ, lặp câu tự động thông minh.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-sky-600 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
              Luyện nghe ngay &rarr;
            </span>
          </a>

          <a href="#" class="group relative rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-emerald-100 overflow-hidden text-left block">
             <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity">
               <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-32 h-32 text-emerald-600"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.5 3.75A1.5 1.5 0 006 5.25v13.5a1.5 1.5 0 001.5 1.5h6a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5V15a.75.75 0 011.5 0v3.75a3 3 0 01-3 3h-6a3 3 0 01-3-3V5.25a3 3 0 013-3h6a3 3 0 013 3V9A.75.75 0 0115 9V5.25a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5h-6zm10.72 4.72a.75.75 0 011.06 0l3 3a.75.75 0 010 1.06l-3 3a.75.75 0 11-1.06-1.06l1.72-1.72H9a.75.75 0 010-1.5h10.94l-1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 010-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 group-hover:bg-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="h-7 w-7"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">Mock Exams</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium mb-6">
              Kho đề thi thử khổng lồ cập nhật mới nhất. Có đồng hồ bấm giờ, chấm điểm tự động và giải thích đáp án chi tiết.
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-bold text-emerald-600 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
              Sắp ra mắt &rarr;
            </span>
          </a>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-white py-12 border-t border-slate-200">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 group mb-6">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">L</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xl font-black text-slate-800 tracking-tight">
            Learn<span class="text-teal-600">Lab</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm">© 2026 Learn Lab. Designed for better learning.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </main>
</Layout>